I'm a moron :(   your initial synaptic paste showed why it didn't want to install. try to install it using aptitude, it should give you an explanation how that lyrics package prevents the install. sorry

aptitude install <banshee thing> should tell you why it doesn't want to install. usually you have to remove the lyrics package first, then you can
